---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About WindowPlant Lab and the 30-day traffic experiment behind the site."
  canonicalPath="/about/"
>
  <article class="content">
    <h1>About WindowPlant Lab</h1>
    <p>
      WindowPlant Lab is a 30-day website traffic experiment focused on one practical question:
      where should a renter put a houseplant so it has a fair chance?
    </p>
    <p>
      The site does not claim professional horticultural credentials or personal testing that has not happened.
      Pages label assumptions, practical heuristics, and future measurement opportunities.
    </p>
    <h2>Experiment goals</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Earn independently verifiable search impressions and organic clicks.</li>
      <li>Publish useful tools and checklists, not generic volume content.</li>
      <li>Learn which pages, queries, and utilities create real human visits.</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
